title: Godin Artisan ST til sölu
text:
- Maple top, rosewood fingerboard
- Schaller Floyd Rose
- Original pickups with coil split
- Original list price was well over $1000 in 1992
I paid about 65.000 + tax for this rare guitar, but I will sell it at 40.000 which is a really shit price for a great guitar but hey, tough times and its got to go quick. PM me.
